<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
    lang="en"
    metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_template/master"
    i18n:domain="doap">
<body>
<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1>Welcome to DOAP!</h1>

    <p>This is the Description of a Project web service, where we catalogue
    all the open source projects registered in The Launchpad. You can read
    more about the "Description Of A Project" framework
    <a href="+about">here</a>. We urge you to register your open source
    project with The Launchpad.</p>

	<ul>
        <li><a href="projects/">View Projects</a>: see a list of the
        projects that have been registered in The Launchpad.</li>
		<li><a href="projects/+search">Search Projects</a>: find a project
        using a keyword search across the project names, titles and
        descriptions.</li>
        <li><a href="projects/+new">Create a New Project</a>: register a new
        project with The Launchpad.</li>
	</ul>

</div>
</body>
</html>

